-- Coal of Africa Seeks Makhado Partner in South Africa, Business Day Says
-- B y   A n t o n y   S g u a z z i n
-- 2010-11-30T04:43:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-30/coal-of-africa-seeks-makhado-partner-in-south-africa-business-day-says.html
Coal of Africa Ltd. will seek a
partner to help it develop its Makhado coal mine, which will
cost about $400 million, Johannesburg’s Business Day reported,
citing John Wallington, the company’s chief executive officer.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
